# Learner state is PERSONAL, MUTABLE runtime data — never committed (PR-9).
# The engine (cc_spine/learner_state.py) and schemas are committed; the state is not.
# Synthetic fixtures under spine/tests/fixtures/ are the ONLY learner-state-shaped data
# allowed in the repo (they carry no real study history and no PII).
.local/
spine/learner-state/
learner_state.json
*.learner-state.json

# API-generated variant DRAFTS are local runtime data (PR-10.4b) — never committed.
# The sanctioned home is .local/variant-drafts/ (covered by .local/ above); these
# belt-and-braces patterns catch a draft parked anywhere else.
spine/variant-drafts/
*.variant-draft.json
*.draft.key.json
